<title>16 页的小册子</title>
<steps>
 <item>
  <p>
   Press the menu button in the top-right corner of the window and press the <gui style="button">Print</gui> button.
  </p>
 </item>
 <item>
  <p>选择 <gui>常规</gui> 标签页。</p>
  <p>在 <em>范围</em> 中，选择 <gui>页面</gui>。</p>
  <tree>
   <item>
   Type the numbers of the pages in this order:
       <item>16, 1, 2, 15, 14, 3, 4, 13, 12, 5, 6, 11, 10, 7, 8, 9</item>
    </item>
  </tree>
 </item>
 <item>
  <p>选择 <gui>页面设置</gui> 标签页。</p>
  <p>
   Under <em>Layout</em>, in the <gui>Two-sided</gui> menu, select <gui>Short Edge (Flip)</gui>.
  </p>
  <p>在 <gui>每面页数</gui> 菜单中，选择 <gui>2</gui>。</p>
  <p>在 <gui>页面顺序</gui> 菜单中，选择 <gui>从左到右</gui>。</p>
 </item>
 <item>
  <p>单击 <gui>打印</gui>。</p>
 </item>
</steps>
